description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Bank Podiatrist&lt;br /&gt; Farnham and surrounding area&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you looking for flexible NHS bank opportunities to fit around your lifestyle? Do you want to decide when and where you work, and where currently 94% of those using our services would recommend us to care for their friend or family? If so, this could be the place for you. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Feel Valued&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;As a Bank Podiatrist, you’ll be working as part of the NHS system where we deliver services across North East Hants, Farnham and Surrey Heath.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;As well as the attractive hourly rates of pay, you’ll benefit from:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Working in an environment focused on the highest clinical and quality standards with 91% of our services being rated overall&lt;strong&gt; good&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;outstanding&lt;/strong&gt; by the CQC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Flexible hours either full time or part time, allowing you to achieve the best &lt;strong&gt;work / life balance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Opportunities to work in different areas and various different services to gain new knowledge and experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Access to our Strive for Better networks, a national support and professional network made up of NHS professionals like you, giving you the chance to &lt;strong&gt;constantly develop industry-leading care and quality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Free statutory and mandatory training, as well as access to a range of courses and e-learning to develop further skills, &lt;strong&gt;continuing your professional development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Access to our free well-being service available 24/7/365 online and by telephone including; counsellors, post trauma incident support, legal, debt and practical life management helpline, guided self-help, telephonic career coaching and monthly well-being newsletters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Access to NHS discount, the option to join the NHS pension scheme, free on-site parking, free uniform, access to online pay slips, fully paid induction, free parking, access to information on permanent vacancies as well as extras such as free hot and cold drinks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Feel Proud&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;At Farnham Hospital you’ll join a team who are enthusiastic and caring with a “good” CQC rating. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;As a bank Podiatrist you will manage a mixed caseload of children and adults undertaking wound care, msk, nail surgery and routine treatments.   Working within the Podiatry team, you will provide assessment and intervention for complex and high risk patients. You will support the supervision and training of students, and podiatry assistants. You’ll care for patients and their families in the way that you believe is best, delivering our high service standards, sharing best practice, and actively improving the way we work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Feel Inspired&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We partner with the NHS and Local Authorities to deliver services which make a positive difference to the people working in them and relying on them. We don’t run private clinics, and Richard Branson has confirmed that if and when we make a profit in the future, he’ll re-invest it back into those services. In fact, we’ve never made a profit from publicly funded services and Virgin Group has invested £60m of additional funding which has helped ensure we can deliver high quality, sustainable and modern services and support the communities we serve.  &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Feel the Difference&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you are a Podiatrist with a degree in Podiatry and HCPC registration we’d love to talk to you about having you join the team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you’d like to discuss the role further, or request the full job description, please contact Angela Masson via email: angela.masson@virgincare.co.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Virgin Care&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We’re committed to equal opportunities and welcome a broad diversity of talent to apply. We reserve the right to cease any advertising prior to the published closing date for a role that receives a high number of applications. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;As a Disability Confident Committed company, we work in partnership with the Department of Work and Pensions (DWP) to provide facilities, work environment adjustments and technical solutions to make our business an inclusive place for all.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Virgin Care Limited, its subsidiary companies and the Virgin Care LLPs are part of the Virgin Group and provide publicly funded health and social care services. If you would like to know a little more about how we use your information, please see our website’s privacy policy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
